OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FProposed rental reforms to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fallow pets in properties   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Animal shelters have hailed a proposed 
OL,6, law that would allow tenants to keep   
OL,7, pets in rental properties as a "game   
OL,8, changer".                              
OL,10,FIt would give tenants the legal right  
OL,11,Fto request a pet in their home, which  
OL,12,Flandlords cannot unreasonably refuse.  
OL,14,FThe change is a part of a wide-range of
OL,15,Fproposed rental reforms including the  
OL,16,Fabolition of no-fault evictions.       
OL,18,FBut one landlord's association wants   
OL,19,Fmore information on the circumstances  
OL,20,Fin which landlords can refuse pets.    
